articles.author: Danny Goodwin
articles.title: 20 most profitable Google queries revealed during antitrust trial - Search Engine Land
articles.description: iPhone and car insurance related search terms made Google the most revenue, according to a new trial exhibit.
articles.content: Ever wondered which search queries drive the most revenue for Google? It turns out that iPhone, insurance and cheap flight queries drove the most revenue for Google in the U.S., at least for one week… [+1323 chars]
